SUMMARY:Pelvic Floor 101: Strong\, Supported\, and In Control
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Your pelvic floor plays a major role in movement\, stability\,
  and everyday comfortbut most people barely think about it! Join us for th
 is informative dive into one of the bodys most important support systems. 
 Learn what your pelvic floor actually does \, signs it may need some TLC\,
  when you need to seek out professional help and practical exercises you c
 an start using right away. Whether youre curious\, dealing with symptoms\,
  or just want to feel stronger and more confident in your body\, this talk
  will give you the knowledge and tools to take control of your pelvic heal
 th. July 15\, 2026 Julie Blacker DPT 12-12:45 pm Register Here (https:even
 ts.teams.microsoft.comevent92f8d00b-e528-4736-9bd3-b3100cea4efd599ceff3-02
 a8-45bc-baef-c48cb8be94c4) ( Once you register the link will be sent\, ple
 ase save to log into event) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/1911
 46
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/191146
END:VEVENT
