DESCRIPTION:From this presentation\, you will understand what blood sugar 
 is and how its used in our bodies\, learn how different foods impact blood
  sugar levels\, and identify healthy eating patterns that may help keep yo
 ur blood sugar under better control. Register: Healthier Blood Sugar July 
 15 This presentation counts toward the Wellness Incentives - 100quarter \n
