SUMMARY:BayCare Presents: Diabetes Trifecta- Awareness\, Eating\, and Ever
 yday Action
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Diabetes and prediabetes are more common than ever  but small 
 daily choices can make a big difference. This engaging session focuses on 
 understanding personal risk\, simplifying healthy eating\, and incorporati
 ng realistic everyday actions that support better blood sugar control and 
 overall health. August 13\, 2026 Martie Hale RDN 12- 12:45 pm Register Her
 e (https:events.teams.microsoft.comeventd0badb0c-f7eb-4316-941d-03bac31944
