SUMMARY:BayCare Presents - Gratitude and Mental Wellness: The Science of T
 hankfulness
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Gratitude isnt just a feel-good emotionits a powerful tool for
  enhancing mental health and overall well-being. This engaging webinar wil
 l delve into how gratitude can reduce stress\, improve mood\, strengthen r
 elationships\, and foster resilience. Participants will learn practical st
 rategies for cultivating gratitude in daily life\, both personally and pro
 fessionally\, and discover how small shifts in perspective can lead to las
 ting improvements in mental health. Join us to unlock the science behind t
 hankfulness and take steps toward a more balanced\, joyful mindset. Click 
